title: june 29: oh my iPhone!
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the introduction of the iPhone. After, she reflects on the fifth studio album from Drake. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
